<li><strong><a href=3D"https://livesimply.me/how-to-make-homemade-floor-cle=
aner-2-ways/">DIY floor cleaner</a></strong></li>



<li><strong><a href=3D"https://livesimply.me/how-to-make-homemade-glass-and=
-mirror-cleaner/">glass cleaner</a></strong></li>



<li><strong>and the list goes on=E2=80=A6</strong></li>
</ul>



<p>One of my favorite DIY products to make is candles using soy wax or bees=
wax. </p>



<p><strong>I=E2=80=99ve been making homemade candles for years now and they=
=E2=80=99ve quickly become the #1 requested homemade gift</strong> that we =
give out during the holiday season. I love adding natural candles to my hom=
e, both for the cozy ambiance and scent.</p>
</div></div>



<div class=3D"wp-block-group"><div class=3D"wp-block-group__inner-container=
