<li><strong>Small cooking pot/saucepan</strong>: You=E2=80=99ll fill this p=
ot with water to make a double boiler. The wax will<em> not</em> come into =
contact with this pot, so use what you have in the kitchen.</li>



<li><strong>Wax melting pot: </strong>Such as a medium-size <strong><a href=
=3D"https://amzn.to/3rkW83v" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"nofollow">glass mixin=
g bowl</a></strong>, <strong><a href=3D"https://amzn.to/46qrWTn" target=3D"=
