never be able to use this pot for anything other than candle making, as the=
 wax will adhere to the pot and be difficult to scrape off and remove.&nbsp=
;</li>



<li><strong>2  8-ounce heat-safe jars:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://amz=
