 use  4 4-ounce jars for smaller candles. Any kind of high-rimmed, heat-pro=
of jar will work for candle making.&nbsp;</li>



<li><strong>2&nbsp;<a href=3D"http://amzn.to/2i1hQVg" target=3D"_blank" rel=
=3D"noreferrer noopener nofollow">clothespins</a>&nbsp;or mechanical pencil=
s:</strong> For keeping the tall wicks upright in the jars. </li>



<li><strong>2&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://amzn.to/2Poval0" target=3D"_blank" re=
