				<div class=3D"comment-content">
					<p>Listed below are simple steps using which you can make your own hom=
emade scented candle:<br>
Start by preparing a clean and flat surface covered with a newspaper or tow=
el<br>
Second measure the amount of wax required to fill the container<br>
Start melting the wax by pouring it into the double boiler<br>
Add the fragrance oil and stir for few seconds, it will provide an exquisit=
e floral smell<br>
Attache a wick to the bottom of the container before you start to pour the =
melted wax<br>
Use chopsticks to secure the wick so that it remains centered until the wax=
 solidifies<br>
Wait for few seconds, once the temperature reaches 140 Degrees pour the wax=
 into the container</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

